mixin faceDanger()
  - var values = { title: 'Face Danger', name: 'FaceDanger', class: 'face-danger', page: 'page X', radio: 'face_danger', stat: `?{Stat|Edge&#44;@{edge}|Iron&#44;@{iron}|Heart&#44;@{heart}|Shadow&#44;@{shadow}|Wits&#44;@{wits}|Essence - Invoke&#44;?{Essence&amp;#124;0&amp;#125;&#125;`, stat_repeat: '?{Stat}', roll: true}
  +container(values)
    p When you attempt something risky or react to an imminent threat, envision your action and roll. If you act...
    ul
      li With speed, agility, or precision: Roll +edge.
      li With charm, loyalty, or courage: Roll +heart.
      li With aggressive action, forceful defense, strength, or endurance: Roll +iron.
      li With deception, stealth, or trickery: Roll +shadow.
      li With expertise, insight, or observation: Roll +wits.
    p On a strong hit, you are successful. Take +2 momentum.
    p On a weak hit, you succeed, but face a troublesome cost. Choose one.
    ul
      li You are delayed, lose advantage, or face a new danger: Suffer -1 momentum (-2 if you used a shield).
      li Your shield loses durability: Reduce its Face Danger/Clash addition by 1.
      li You are tired or hurt: Endure Harm (1d3P harm).
      li You are dispirited or afraid: Endure Stress (1 stress).
      li You sacrifice resources: Suffer -1 supply or -1 wealth.
      li You get a negative condition: Take a condition.
    p On a miss, you fail, or your progress is undermined by a dramatic and costly turn of events. Pay the Price. If you are in combat.

