mixin gatherInformation()
  - var values = { title: 'Gather Information', name: 'GatherInformation', class: 'gather-information', page: 'page X', radio: 'gather_information', stat: ``, stat_repeat: '', roll: true }
  +container(values)
    p When you search an area, ask questions, conduct an investigation, or follow a track, roll +wits. If you act within a community or ask questions of a person with whom you share a bond, add +2.
    p On a strong hit, you discover something helpful and specific. The path you must follow or action you must take to make progress is made clear. Envision what you learn, and take +4 momentum.
    p On a weak hit, you discover something helpful, but the information complicates your quest or a new danger is introduced. Envision what you discover, and take +2 momentum.
    p On a miss, your investigation unearths a dire threat or reveals an unwelcome truth that undermines your quest. Pay the Price.

mixin undertakeAJourney()
  - var values = { title: 'Undertake a Journey', name: 'UndertakeAJourney', class: 'undertake-a-journey', page: 'page X', radio: 'undertake_a_journey', stat: ``, stat_repeat: '', roll: true }
  +container(values)
    p When you travel across hazardous or unfamiliar lands, set the rank of your journey.
    ul
      li Troublesome journey: 3 progress per waypoint.
      li Dangerous journey: 2 progress per waypoint.
      li Formidable journey: 1 progress per waypoint.
      li Extreme journey: 2 ticks per waypoint.
      li Epic journey: 1 tick per waypoint.
    p Then, for each segment of your journey, roll +wits. If you are setting off from a community with which you share a bond, add +2 to your initial roll.
    p If you are making this move for the fourth time, without having done the Make Camp move or Sojourn move, take a condition as appropriate to the circumstances.
    p On a strong hit, choose one.
    ul
      li You make good use of your resources: Mark progress and take +2 momentum.
      li You move with scrutiny: Mark progress and Find an Opportunity.
      li You move at speed: Mark progress twice and take +1 momentum, but suffer -1 supply.
    p On a weak hit, choose one.
    ul
      li You go as expected: Mark progress, but suffer -1 supply.
      li You move with precaution: Mark progress and Find an Opportunity, but suffer -1 supply and -2 momentum.
      li You move at speed, but with a cost: Mark progress twice and take +1 momentum, but suffer -2 supply and Reveal a Danger.
      li You explore: Find an Opportunity, but suffer -1 momentum.
    p On a miss, you have gone hopelessly astray, your objective is lost to you, or you were misled about your destination. If your journey continues, clear all but one filled progress, and raise the journey's rank by one (if not already epic).

